column2: Please provide a title page. Your submission should include a front page which states the full title of the manuscript, and the full names of each author in alphabetical order together with their affilliation and email address.

Please ensure identifiable data are obsfucated. Your manuscript contains information which may reveal a patients identity. Identifiable data must be removed in your revision in order to proceed with your submission. Please follow the journal guidelines with regards to which data must be removed.

Please include an Acknowledgements section. The Acknowledgements section should be located with the backmatter at the end of your submission. This section should acknowledge any parties who have assisted with the research but have not contributed as an author. If you have no acknowledgements, please state this in the Acknowledgements section.
